Name: Catcher in the Tide
AttributesDescription: A special reward obtained from the "Tidal Defense Simulator" event. It records the highest TD waves you withstood in the "Total Defense Test."
BgDescription: Just as you once witnessed in the simulation, that towering tide will one day descend, engulfing all. But this time, you are ready to face it again.
